* This wasn't going good!
Iron Raptor hissed as Prowl's claws came away from her back, red mech-fluid 
flowing from the deep wounds while she tried to keep a steady hold on his 
foot that she mannaged to catch hold of.
Prowl was already plumeting towards the earth by the time she landed back to 
it from her jump, but then something caught her by surprise.
He'd switched back and sank his front claws into her back now instead, her 
eyes only catching the sight of his teeth as he went for her neck.
< Slag!>
Iron Raptor tried to move her head out of the way so that she would avoid 
those sharp teeth but she mooved to slow and he got the back of it. 
But...not before she made a go at his wings.
If she broke a wing there was no chance of him lifting off into the air and 
getting a drop on her, which could finish her if he didn't already on the 
ground.
HIS mode was bigger and more heavily muscled then hers, but her own beast 
mode wasn't just a close combat weapon. It had it's specialties that she 
hoped she could use.
But later.*
